Buzz Number:- If a number is divisible by 7 or else leaves a remainder of 7 when divide by 10

Using Java... :-
import java.util.Scanner;
public class BuzzNumber{
    public static void main(String[]args){
        Scanner sc= new Scanner(System.in);
        System.out.println("Enter a number: ");
        int n=sc.nextInt();
        if(n%7==0 || n%10==0)
        {
            System.out.println("Given number is a Buzz Number");
        }
        else
            System.out.println("Given number is not a Buzz Number");
    }
}

Using Python... :-
N=input("Enter a number: ");
N=int(N);

if(N%7==0 or N%10==7):
print("Given number is Buzz Number");
else:
print("Given number is not Buzz Number");
 
